data.oai_dc:dc: Major Roads, Baltimore City BES ID 88-

Major Roads for Baltimore City. No metadata was provided with this dataset, the UVM Spatial Analysis Lab has attempted to evaluate this dataset and generate metadata. When compared to high-resolution imagery and other transportation datasets positional inaccuracies were observed. As a result caution should be taken when using this dataset. For the best available transportation data use the Roads_GDT_MSA dataset.
